name: 1997 Mixtape
description:
I grew up listening to a lot music.  That translated into making my own mixtapes for friends and family.  The art of the mixtape is a lost art and I wanted to create something that paid respect to an artform that meant so much to me.  

COLLECTORS ***Please DM proof of purchase on twitter and I will share the actual mixtape playlist I put together on applemusic.  I guarantee you either make out with someone you are attracted to or laugh until you throw up from the musical selections.  Either way its gonna be a good time!
